tegaki-wagomu
=============

A simple handwriting recognition engine based on DTW and k-NN.

Requirements
------------

Python        2.4    http://www.python.org
tegaki-python 0.3   

Install
-------

$ python setup.py build
($ su)
# python setup.py install

Developer
---------

If you intend to contribute to this engine, the most convenient way to install
it is to add the following to your ~/.bashrc file.

tegakiroot=/path/to/hwr/
export PYTHONPATH=$tegakiroot/tegaki-engines/tegaki-wagomu/src:$PYTHONPATH

